description: A row of umbrellas line the edge of the street along with chairs and what appears to be vendor booths. Midway down the street, a large brown tarp is visible and appears to be securing property or merchandise while a man sits in a chair with his back to the bungle secured by the brown tarp.
The bench is on a brick patio in front of the white house with the tan roof that has a white SUV parked in the driveway.
